Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
AboutPanel AboutPanel is the class to show who developed the program.
Article Article is the class representing a PmWiki article with text, images and files.
Attachment Attachment is the class to save files or images being on an article page in the Article class.
GUI GUI is the class to be able to use pm2media with a graphical user interface.
MediaWiki MediaWiki is the class representing a MediaWiki installation.
MultiPartFormOutputStream MultiPartFormOutputStream is used to write "multipart/form-data" to a java.net.URLConnection for POSTing.
Pm2Media Pm2Media is the class configuring the whole pm2media project.
PmWiki PmWiki is the class representing a PmWiki installation.
PmWiki2MediaWikiConverter PmWiki2MediaWikiConverter is the class to handle conversion of PmWiki syntax to MediaWiki syntax.
SyntaxPair SyntaxPair is the class representing a pair of equivalent PmWiki and MediaWiki syntax.
